Class DataModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • ext.ojalgo.pride.Resolver
      • ext.ojalgo.pride.DataModel
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class DataModel
extends Resolver

    DataModel is responsible for creating DataAccessObject instances, and resolving data relationships (foreign keys in the database).

    All applications must instantiate a subclass of DataModel and register the necessary business object factories.

    Author:
    apete
